            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S.) In nomine sancte et individue Trinitatis. <persName
                            key="#Countess #childOf #Salian #Mansi #Offersio/donatio #Public_rituals"
                            ref="#people/125">Matilda</persName> Dei gratia <rs key="#Countess"
                            >comitissa</rs>, <rs key="#childOf">filia</rs> quondam <rs
                            key="#Marquis/duke">marchionis</rs>
                        <persName key="#Marquis/duke #parentOf" ref="#people/1">Bonifacii</persName>
                        si quid est, lege <rs key="#Salian">Salica</rs> vivens presentibus dixi:
                        Quisquis in sanctis et venerabilibus locis aliquid de suis contulerit rebus
                        iuxta auctoris vocem centuplum accipiet et vitam possidebit eternam. Ideoque
                        ego qui supra Matilda comitissa dono et offero et concedo a presenti die in
                        antea <rs key="#Monasteries #Abbots #Mansi #Offersio/donatio"
                            >monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti Benedicti
                            iuxta Larionem</orgName> cui <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/2189"
                            >Albericus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> preesse videtur, pro mercede anime mee et
                        parentum meorum, videlicet <rs key="#Mansi">mansum unum</rs> in <placeName
                            key="#Islands" ref="#places/2981"><rs key="#Islands">insula</rs>
                            Reveris</placeName> positum cum <rs key="#Forests">bosco</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder #Animals">babulo</rs> cum omni honore et <rs
                            key="#Districtio">distriscto</rs> cuius confinia hec sunt: a meridie
                            <placeName ref="#places/2417">Custellum</placeName>, a mane <orgName
                            key="#Mother_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/1426"><rs
                                key="#Mother_churches">episcopium</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Mother_churches" ref="#places/275"
                                >Mantuanensis</placeName> ecclesie</orgName>, a nulla hora
                        Valmarcia, a sero iuris predicte comitisse; una cum accessionibus et
                        ingressionibus et superioribus et inferioribus suis in integrum dono,
                        offero, concedo et trado in perpetuum ad habendum predicto monasterio. <rs
                            key="#Public_rituals">Insuper per cultellum, festucum nodatum, vuantonem
                            et vuasonem terre atque ramum arboris ad proprietatem ipsius monasterii
                            reliqui</rs>; et faciat predicta ecclesia quicquid voluerit sine mea
                        meorumque heredum et proheredum repetitione et molestatione, cum omni iure
                        et districto prephate sicut supra legitur. Si quis vero contra hanc <rs
                            key="#Offersio/donatio">cartulam nostre offersionis concessionis et
                            donationis</rs> quandoque ire vel agere temptaverit aut per quodvis
                        ingenium infringere quesierit, <rs key="#Penalty">libras denariorum
                            Papiensium quinquaginta</rs> componat, partem <rs
                            key="#Camera #Camera_regis #Camera_of_other_public_authorities">camere
                            fisci</rs>, reliquam monasterio iniuriam passo, et hanc presens cartulam
                        firmam semper permaneat cum stipulacione subnixa. Et pergamena manibus meis
                        de terra levavi, et <persName key="#Notary #Writer #Offersio/donatio"><name
                                ref="Martinus">Martino</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notario</rs> Sacri Palacii tradidi et scribere rogavi.
                        Actum in <geogName key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/42"><rs key="#Curtes"
                                >curte</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Curtes" ref="#places/34"
                            >Pigogange</placeName></geogName> feliciter, anno millesimo centesimo
                        terciodecimo indicione VI. Matilda Dei gratia si quid est subscripsi. Huius
                        rei <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs>
                        <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio #Causidicus" ref="#people/3530">Odaldus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Causidicus">causidicus</rs>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio">Rodulfus</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio" ref="#people/2194">Amedeus</persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio" ref="#people/3517"
                                >Opizo</persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio" ref="#people/3531"
                            >Petrus</persName> de Comula, <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"
                            >Petrus</persName> di Sala, <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"
                            ref="#people/3525">Rainerius</persName> di Sasso, <persName
                                key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio" ref="#people/3529">Gerardus</persName> de Cornazano,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio" ref="#people/3518"
                            >Gerardus</persName> de Plaza et alii quamplures. Ego Martinus notarius
                        Sacri Palatii hiis interfui er <rs key="#Writer">scripsi</rs>. </ab>
